---
// Por qué nosotros - Features
---
<section id="por-que" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">¿Por qué elegirnos?</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Demo en 24hs</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Te mostramos cómo queda tu negocio online en menos de un día.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 10l4.553-2.276A1 1 0 0121 8.618v6.764a1 1 0 01-1.447.894L15 14M5 18h8a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v8a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Panel Editable</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">El cliente puede cambiar productos, precios y fotos sin saber tecnología.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Stack Estable</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Astro + Sanity + Vercel. Sin plugins que rompan, sin actualizaciones riesgosas.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-orange-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-bold mb-2">Aparecés en Google</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Configuramos Google My Business, Analytics y SEO local para que te encuentren.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>